Package: centralisedapproach
Title: OECD centralised appraoch for distributional wealth estimation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains the functions used in the OECD centralised approach. They combine microdata with national accounts data for a given country and year, in order to construct distributional household wealth estimates. The group of interest, e.g. deciles or percentiles, can be customised.
